# Patterns (Perl regex) of paths under home/ that stow should NOT symlink into
# $HOME. Providing this file REPLACES stow's built-in default ignore list, so
# the stow defaults are reproduced below, plus our own additions.
#
# Why this exists: macOS Finder scatters .DS_Store files everywhere. Without
# this, `stow` tries to link ~/.DS_Store -> the repo copy and aborts the whole
# run on the inevitable conflict with the real (Finder-regenerated) ~/.DS_Store.

# --- our additions ---
\.DS_Store
\._.*

# --- stow's built-in defaults (kept, since this file overrides them) ---
RCS
.+,v
CVS
\.\#.+
\.cvsignore
\.svn
_darcs
\.hg
\.git
\.gitignore
\.gitmodules
.+~
\#.*\#
^/README.*
^/LICENSE.*
^/COPYING
